n data-text=\"Τελίνε\">Τελίνε\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>\u003C/span> τ]ο[ῦ] \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Α\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Α\">Α[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>Γ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>] \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>ΕΠΙΙΕΡΑΠΟΛΟΥ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τελίνε τοῦ Α\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Τελίνε\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Τελίνε\">ΤΕΛΙΝΕ\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>\u003C/span>.]Ο[.]\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Α\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Α\">Α[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>Γ[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text of IG\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2> translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">  \u003C/p>\u003Cp>  \u003C/p>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The name Τηλίνης is attested at Gela in Herodotos 7.153. It seems unlikely that this inscription is genuine: the similar text preserved as ISic001079 = IG XIV.259 is almost certainly a late 18th century fake, and this one appears to have similar context (see principally the discussion of Pareti); the reproduction of the name from Herodotus adds to the doubt. (Note that Carità mis-references this as IG XIV.259.)\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> 1959.0288 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Schubring 1873 75 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002684\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002684\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">258\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Pareti 1914 214-220 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002680\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002680\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Carità 1978 21-22 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002089\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002089\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. \u003C/div>",[216,219,222,225,228,231,234,237],{"id":217,"html":218},"editions","\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\